rows.label: qst703203_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew... Man, I thought that was
the END for me.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0002
rows.name: Thanks for keeping me alive!

rows.label: qst703203_msg0003
rows.name:
You've sure got an appetite.
I'm not sure where you put all that...

rows.label: qst703203_msg0004
rows.name:
Heheh...
My stomach's never let me down!

rows.label: qst703203_msg0005
rows.name:
And also, I love spicy stuff so much
that the more I ate, the more pumped
I got for this whole Drivering deal!

rows.label: qst703203_msg0006
rows.name:
*Gulp*
Just hearing you mention it
makes my insides roil...

rows.label: qst703203_msg0007
rows.name:
...Hey, Rita!
If you think you can laugh it off,
you don't know me very well!

rows.label: qst703203_msg0008
rows.name:
Can you even imagine what would've
happened if these guys weren't here
to help?

rows.label: qst703203_msg0009
rows.name: Aww... I'm sorry, Kaede...

rows.label: qst703203_msg0010
rows.name:
Um, Rita-san... I think Kaede-san is just
worried about you.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0011
rows.name:
As her Driver, you're important to her.
Obviously, she wants you to do well,
and to be well!

rows.label: qst703203_msg0012
rows.name: Kaede-chan... Is that true?

rows.label: qst703203_msg0013
rows.name: Let's head for that big tree next.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0014
rows.name: No answer, huh...?

rows.label: qst703203_msg0015
rows.name:
If you even think about collapsing
again, I'll name this place after you.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0016
rows.name:
"Rita Oasis" has a nice ring to it, don't
you think?

rows.label: qst703203_msg0017
rows.name: Awkward...

rows.label: qst703203_msg0018
rows.name: Erm...

rows.label: qst703203_msg0019
rows.name: Shin, do something..

rows.label: qst703203_msg0020
rows.name: I think this is beyond us now...

rows.label: qst703203_msg0021
rows.name:
Oh I see. Then people will remember
her failure forever.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0022
rows.name: Naturally.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0023
rows.name:
The legend of the bungling greenhorn
Driver who brought shame on her Blade
by collapsing from lack of spicy food!

rows.label: qst703203_msg0024
rows.name:
Stop it! Don't say stuff like that!
I might die of sheer embarrassment...

rows.label: qst703203_msg0025
rows.name: OK, wait up! Kaede-chan, I'm coming!

rows.label: qst703203_msg0026
rows.name:
Thanks, Hikari.
That could have gone a lot worse.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0027
rows.name:
Indeed. Your less-than-tactful
comment might have saved the day.

rows.label: qst703203_msg0028
rows.name: Uh, what? What now? Hey!
